         &none        &none         &hm F2 F2        &none     &kp WNB_STAR &kp MINUS      &hm F11 WNB_EQUAL &hm F4 N4       &hm F5 N5      &hm F6 N6 &kp NB_PLUS   &kp NB_STAR
